<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="A_4._Coding_Standards_47Conventions"> <A name="Section_4."></A>4.  Coding Standards/Conventions </h1>
<span id="TableOfContents"></span>
<div class="foswikiToc" id="foswikiTOC"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Banned_functions_and_syntax"> Banned functions and syntax </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Data_declaration"> Data declaration </a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#General"> General </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Modules"> Modules </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Functions"> Functions </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Subroutines"> Subroutines </a>
</li></ul> 
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Naming_Scheme"> Naming Scheme </a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Indentation_and_line_format"> Indentation and line format </a>
